2005-04-20  Rene Locher
	IDPmisc V0.3.2
	* inf.omit deprecated
	* inf.omit renamed to the more precise name NaRV.omit.
	  NaRV = Not A Regular Value
	* ipairs, iplot, image: densities are now displayed centered over
	  the corresponding factor levels

