2005-10-05 Rene Locher
	IDPmisc V0.4.2
	* ipairs, ilagplot: additional examples on dataset AirQual{SwissAir}
	* Image, ipairs, ilagplot, ixyplot: additional argument
	  'ztransf', which allows transformation of counts by a user
	  defined function.

