	  New arguments 'cex','mgp','tcl'.
	* ipairs: Default distances and character sizes optimized.
	  New arguments 'cex','mgp','tcl'.
	* iplot: Default distances and character sizes optimized.
	  New arguments 'cex','mgp','tcl'.
